snippet.title: Eradicate: futuristic arcade racer for the MS-DOS game jam
snippet.description:
This is a video capture of the unfinished but rather playable version (v0.1) of the DOS arcade racing game I was hacking for the MS-DOS game jam #2: https://itch.io/jam/dos-game-jam-2


There are lots of bugs and missing features, and the only game mode available is time trial with a single sparsely-populated track.


You can download the source code and binaries from github (see "releases"): http://github.com/MutantStargoat/eradicate or the game jam submission page: https://itch.io/jam/dos-game-jam-2/rate/638563
